<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA17">
<l>kāṇpārkkuṅ kāṇalān taṉmaiyaṉē kaitoḻutu</l>
<l>kāṇpārkkuṅ kāṇalāṅ kātalāṟ - kāṇpārkkuc</l>
<l>cōtiyāyc cintaiyuḷē tōṉṟumē tollulakuk</l>
<l>kātiyāy niṉṟa varaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who look out there is seeing the nature, there is seeing</l>
<l>for those who look out with love, hands [folded] in worship, he appears</l>
<l>inside the minds of those who look out as a light,</l>
<l>Hara who stands there as the beginning of the old world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
